<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.7">
<l>iruṅkai matakaḷi ṟīrkkiṉ ṟavaṉai</l>
<l>paruṅkip paṟittukkoṇ ṭōṭum paramaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>neruṅku pavaḷamum nērnāṇum muttum</l>
<l>maruṅku miruntavā kāṇīrē vāṇuta līrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with bright foreheads, see the way [his] waist</l>
<l>has close-set coral and pearls on the fine [waist] string of the Supreme Being,</l>
<l>who runs, forcibly grasping and killing the one</l>
<l>who drags along the frenzied elephant with a black trunk.</l>
<l>Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
